{
  "id": "adv_main_04_12_01",
  "title": "星空編1章56話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kohei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "もしもし。はい……それが、トリエルはかなり先まで\nスケジュールが埋まっていまして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-end-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9330.2494558,
          "startTime": 15.2969161225
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kohei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "月ストとサニピも予定が詰まっているので……\nはい、申し訳ありません。それでは失礼します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5400,
          "startTime": 17
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kohei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "次はメールチェックか……。出演依頼が山のように\nきているな。これ全部に返事していたら夜になるぞ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.6620323658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、VENUSグランプリが\n終わってからずっと忙しそうですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.3378913562,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "今年のVENUSグランプリ……特別賞を\n取るくらい、星見プロのアイドルが大活躍だった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.8045580228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "あの大会を見れば……\n星見プロに出演依頼が殺到するのも当然……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.4616600238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 45.7378913562
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "テレビ、イベント、ライブと日本中から引っ張りだこで\nしばらくはのんびりする暇もなさそうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.9378913562,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスとリズノワなんて\n海外からもオファーがきているそうですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.1712229093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロの活動の幅は\n海を越えて広がっていく勢いですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.4045544625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "この勢いで、私達もいつか海外公演するかも……\n夢が広がる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.8712211292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "これから、もっと忙しくなりそうね\nそうなると私達以上に、彼が大変そうだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.6378816923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kohei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "俺の心配はいいから\n三人ともこの後仕事だろ？　時間は大丈夫なのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.3999905904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "あ……\nそろそろ事務所を出ないと、まずいかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.7196483315,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。分刻みで予定が詰まっていますから\n遅刻する訳にはいきません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.5867225331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "では、失礼します\nお仕事、頑張って下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.3200579009,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3266.6666667000045,
          "startTime": 100.5867245676
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kohei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、行ってらっしゃい\n……遙子さん？　どうかしましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.2999900819,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_hrk-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 108.3724990284
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか昔を思い出しちゃって……。私がこんなに\n忙しくなるなんて、あの頃からは信じられないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.5633287283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "君も毎日忙しそうだけど、無理はしないで\nちゃんと体を休めなきゃダメよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.4360670728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kohei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫ですよ\n今の俺は心身共に充実していますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.8130083979,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kohei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それに、今はやりたいことがあるんです\nそれが形になるまでは疲れたなんて言っていられません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.1999900819,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "やりたいこと？\n今度は何を企んでいるのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.9946509117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kohei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_12_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "まだ秘密ですが……遙子さんならきっと\n喜んでくれると思います。楽しみにしていて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.7992192657,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8354.353166700008,
          "startTime": 152.1535724324
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――時は少し遡り",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.8869057657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "VENUSグランプリセミファイナル会場",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.1068966019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
